The,Terremark,vCloud,Express,API,provides,secure,RESTful,access,to,many,of,the,features,and,functions,available,within,the,Terremark,My,Cloud,User,Interface,The,RESTful,API,is,compatible,with,most,programming,and,scripting,languages,Since,the,vCloud,Express,API,extends,control,over,the,My,Cloud,User,Interface,it,has,additional,security,to,protect,your,account,against,unauthorized,access,Access,to,the,RESTful,API,is,secured,via,SSL,and,your,My,Cloud,user,credentials,With,the,vCloud,Express,API,you,can,programmatically,scale,out,your,servers,by,invoking,our,copy,server,feature,or,simply,reconfigure,your,servers,to,add,more,CPU,memory,and,storage,to,scale,up,Or,use,the,API,to,manipulate,your,load,balancer,and,Internet,settings,to,control,traffic,to,your,applications